  "title": "Financial Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This commission-based role offers a career track defined by autonomy, where your income reflects the value you provide. You will build a scalable financial advisory practice by delivering trusted, client-centric advice that transcends transactional sales.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and deliver strategic financial advice that addresses clients’ long-term goals and builds lasting trust</li><li>Translate complex financial concepts into clear, actionable guidance to enhance client confidence and decision-making</li><li>Build and manage your financial advisory practice as a scalable business, leveraging systems, regulatory frameworks, and operational support provided</li><li>Demonstrate resilience and accountability by taking ownership of your career growth and client outcomes</li><li>Collaborate with mentors to continuously develop skills aligned with your learning style and career objectives</li><li>Foster client relationships by prioritizing service and ethical advisory practices over short-term transactions</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Evidence of resilience and excellence demonstrated through academic achievements, leadership roles, sales experience, or sports</li><li>Client-centric mindset with the ability to view sales as a form of service</li><li>High personal agency and accountability in managing professional responsibilities and career development</li></ul>",
